OL,3,CRules on waste tyres tightened as
OL,4,Cmillions dumped at illegal furnaces in
OL,5,CIndia
OL,7,FMillions of UK waste tyres are taken
OL,8,Fto makeshift furnaces in India and
OL,9,Fomitting toxic fumes, according to the
OL,10,FEnvironment Agency.
OL,12,FThe environment watchdog has said it
OL,13,Fwill tighten rules around exporting
OL,14,Fwaste tyres after official figures
OL,15,Fsuggested 25 million tyres, around
OL,16,F350,000 tonnes, are sent to India
OL,17,Fannually.
