OL,3,CRules on waste tyres tightened as
OL,4,Cmillions dumped at illegal furnaces in
OL,5,CIndia
OL,7,FUsed tyres can be shipped overseas for
OL,8,Frecycling under UK waste regulations,
OL,9,Fbut an Environmental Agency review
OL,10,Fpublished on Friday suggested millions
OL,11,Fwere going to unregulated dumps or
OL,12,Fillegal industrial plants.
