OL,3,CRules on waste tyres tightened as
OL,4,Cmillions dumped at illegal furnaces in
OL,5,CIndia
OL,7,FIt said it is "highly likely" that a
OL,8,Fproportion of UK waste tyres were
OL,9,Ftaken to sites in India illegally to
OL,10,Fundergo a heating process that
OL,11,Freleases carcinogenic gasses and heavy
OL,12,Fmetals, known as pyrolysis.
OL,14,FThe review said concerns were raised
OL,15,Fover whether it was fulfilling its
OL,16,Flegal obligation for overseeing the
OL,17,Fexport of UK waste tyres to India.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
