OL,3,CRules on waste tyres tightened as
OL,4,Cmillions dumped at illegal furnaces in
OL,5,CIndia
OL,7,FIt added that it "cannot assume" based
OL,8,Fon the incomplete information it held
OL,9,Fthat tyres are being properly
OL,10,F"recovered in an environmentally sound
OL,11,Fmanner", as required under rules set
OL,12,Fout by UK waste shipment.
OL,14,FThe regulator recognised it "should
OL,15,Ftake further steps" to ensure it is
OL,16,Ffulfilling its overseas legal
OL,17,Fobligations and pledged it would carry
OL,18,Fout "enhanced export verification
OL,19,Fchecks" to India from October 1.
