OL,3,CRules on waste tyres tightened as
OL,4,Cmillions dumped at illegal furnaces in
OL,5,CIndia
OL,7,FIt means operators arranging shipments
OL,8,Fto India must demonstrate the waste
OL,9,Ftyres are being recovered in an
OL,10,Fenvrionmentally sound manner.
OL,12,FThe agency added it will use its legal
OL,13,Fpowers to prevent certain shipments if
OL,14,Fit is "not satisfied with the evidence
OL,15,Fprovided".
