OL,3,CRules on waste tyres tightened as
OL,4,Cmillions dumped at illegal furnaces in
OL,5,CIndia
OL,7,FAn Environment Agency spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Following concerns raised
OL,9,Faround waste exports, the Environment
OL,10,FAgency has completed a review into its
OL,11,Fapproach for regulating the export of
OL,12,Fwaste tyres.
OL,14,F"We are taking direct action based on
OL,15,Fthe review's findings and will launch
OL,16,Fenhanced verification checks for all
OL,17,Fwaste tyres exported to India to
OL,18,Fensure they are handled in an
OL,19,Fenvironmentally sound manner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
